title: Team or Duo Ranked games
body:
Looking for a group or some one to play ranked with. I main support but can play adc,or mid. I am currently bronze 2 from placement.
Highest i have got was gold 5 in previous sessions. Send us a invite even if its just for normal's.

highest so far was silver 2 in last season
